_News\"}, {\"begin\": 664, \"end\": 674, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Dixon\", \"score\": 0.9999738152345728, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Nick Dixon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Dixon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nick_Dixon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stop changing the flag.\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 720, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They think they can just do what they want with the flag.\", \"from\": 721, \"to\": 778, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Who are these people?\", \"from\": 779, \"to\": 800, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Simon Evans explained: \\\"I know the origins of our flag.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 857, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 802, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Evans_(comedian)\", \"score\": 0.8357815444741087, \"rank\": 0.10557184750731503, \"text\": \"Simon Evans\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Evans_(comedian)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Simon_Evans_(comedian)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is the three national flags that were joined together in the Union.\", \"from\": 858, \"to\": 928, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not just made up by some design agency they think that very ancient adherence to the patron saint, is absolutely despicable.\", \"from\": 929, \"to\": 1058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just do not know what's getting into these design agencies at the moment.\", \"from\": 1060, \"to\": 1136, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It does feel like significant political decisions and movements and provocations coming from the most trivial commercial sources.\\\"\", \"from\": 1137, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"WATCH CLIP ABOVE FOR MORE\", \"from\": 1269, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": []}]}"